criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. age at study enrolment 6 to 12 years

          2. healthy; no known history of major medical illnesses and taking no chronic
             medications;

          3. residence at the respective study site for 12 months or longer;

          4. no use of iodine containing dietary supplements during the last 6 months;

          5. no use of X-ray / CT contrast agent or iodine containing medication within the last
             year.
